config:
1- run => npm i
2- firebase/firebaseConfig => copy firebase config for web
3- run => firebase init
>>> ready to start!!

dev:
1- run => npm start
2- run => sass:watch
3- run => firebase serve
>>> ready to dev!!

prod:
1- run => npm run prod
2- index.html => change to <script src prod>
3- index.html => change <script src prod> name to something like -prod.bundle010119.js
4- prod.bundle => change prod.bunlde name in the same name
5- run => firebase deploy [--only functions | hosting | storage]
>>> ready to go!!